{"tid":2397791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首外交演說 強調修復盟國關係  拜登宣告美國回來 「華是最難纏競爭者」","createTime":"2021-02-06T17:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:04:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb77d712d93d819512b70fb675f039b172f7d7d","tid":2397791,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/EOFE2CBQTJFPRB5UJMRUEXVPR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FEOFE2CBQTJFPRB5UJMRUEXVPR4%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=4094f8cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FEOFE2CBQTJFPRB5UJMRUEXVPR4%2F&h=9de7abd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210206/EOFE2CBQTJFPRB5UJMRUEXVPR4/</a><br />\n<br />\n首外交演說 強調修復盟國關係 <br />\n拜登宣告美國回來 「華是最難纏競爭者」<br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：斥彈劾違憲 特朗普拒作供<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登發表上任以來首場重要外交政策演說，宣佈美國過了四年脫軌日子後，如今回到世界外交舞台，強調會致力修復與盟國關係，預示會進取應對中國、俄羅斯兩大威權的挑戰，抑制中俄野心，特別矢言會對抗中國經濟濫權、攻擊人權等種種行徑，但亦會在符合美國利益事務與中國合作。<br />\n<br />\n前日是拜登上任後首度造訪國務院，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美停撐沙地介入也門內戰<br />\n<br />\n拜登形容北京政府是美國「最難纏的競爭對手」，矢言「美國會迎擊中國的經濟濫權，對抗中國攻擊人權、知識產權與環球管理體系&hellip;&hellip;的挑釁和脅迫手段」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XTPt6XgWGogDsmSxR1SOFGeV88k=/3150x2045/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KJ6QXMMCIVAXHKXJ67UWOII2KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXTPt6XgWGogDsmSxR1SOFGeV88k%3D%2F3150x2045%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKJ6QXMMCIVAXHKXJ67UWOII2KM.jpg&h=319ccc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■拜登在國務院發表外交政策演說後，向現場約50人揮手，其他國務院人員透過視像連線觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合美利益 亦可與京合作<br />\n<br />\n然而，正如之前國務卿布林肯講過，美中在競爭中亦有合作可能。拜登說：「只要符合美國利益，我們亦準備好跟北京攜手合作。」<br />\n<br />\n白宮國安顧問蘇利文前日較早時。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「美國之音」引述哈佛大學費正清。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王丹轟重回綏靖主義<br />\n<br />\n現時流亡海外的八九民運領袖王丹，批評拜登是回到綏靖主義，美國和西方將為此付出代價，又指「競爭者」定性不倫不類：競爭雙方守共同規則，惟中共不只不守更破壞規則。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國對港的政策會否因為拜登。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對俄羅斯方面，拜登在講話說：「。。。。。。。。」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登強調外交的重要性，指美國必須重新擁抱維護民主原則的世界。事實上，拜登上場。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n拜登指出，美國面對日益嚴峻的全球挑戰，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社/法新社"},{"pid":"5d3da289a2f9517d7367454027eb842f4415ba7d","tid":2397791,"uid":250654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"講就天下無敵<br />\n亮劍未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a4b4eba17ed9f705221d1c68adf04baac80124","tid":2397791,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d3da289a2f9517d7367454027eb842f4415ba7d","tid":2397791,"uid":250654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"講就天下無敵<br />\n亮劍未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"對俄國亮劍<br />\n含支那碌劍"},{"pid":"3b4d4ea549127491b2e1769a1a395a7b95ebc15b","tid":2397791,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:13:39.000Z","msg":"最難抗拒RMB引誘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeefbf3c3b86372688a2ad7c0e66dc23cdfcb70a","tid":2397791,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"得把口"},{"pid":"3a30c2fdbf96ab746ab9aa38263fd5047b659988","tid":2397791,"uid":12312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0F3VCD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0F3VCD.gif&h=77b7f4ef&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}